ve marketing or promotional information/letters/emails from EZWAGE at any time by simply utilizing the unsubscribe function provided in the profile settings. \n\n  5.4.  Third Party Service Provider. In the event that we engage with third party service providers in connection with our Services, EZWAGE may share Personal Information with such service providers who need access to such information to carry out their work for EZWAGE. Other than such service providers, EZWAGE does not share Personal Information with third parties unless (1) You have indicated to us that you wish to receive information from such parties; (2) You otherwise give us your consent to do so; or (3) in response to a request for information.\n\n  5.5.  Research and Statistical Purposes. We may use certain information you provide for research and statistical purposes and in such cases we will take steps with an aim to protect your individual identity.',
